        testimonial:
          'When it comes to website building and SEO, Ziaflow is very knowledgeable and extremely efficient. They helped me and some of my clients with website consulting and optimization. They are very affordable for small businesses that are growing and startups that need to get a head start.',
        name: 'S.K.',
        job: 'CFO',
      },
      {
        testimonial:
          'I had made a FB post about needing help and this guy in my neighborhood reached out. Come to find out ZiaFlow came through with the clutch performance. They talked me through my issues and reassured me it will all work out. They are true to their word, which speaks volume to me. Thanks, I will be referring you all out.',
        name: 'Richard J.',
        job: 'Owner',
      },
    ]}
    callToAction={{
      target: '_blank',
      text: 'Read more testimonials',
      href: '#',
      icon: 'tabler:chevron-right',
    }}
  />
<ContactUs
    id="form"
    title="Start Your Digital Transformation"
    subtitle="Tell us about your project and we will get back to you within 24 hours. Whether you need custom development, automation, or marketing solutions, our team is ready to help."
    inputs={[
      {
        type: 'text',
        name: 'name',
        label: 'Full Name',
      },
      {
        type: 'email',
        name: 'email',
        label: 'Email',
      },
      {
        type: 'text',
        name: 'company',
        label: 'Company',
      },
      {
        type: 'text',
        name: 'phone',
        label: 'Phone',
      },
    ]}
    textarea={{
      label: 'Tell us about your project',
      placeholder: 'What challenges are you facing? What are your goals? The more details you provide, the better we can help.',
